headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Principal Financial Group After Strong Multi Year Share Price Gains
summary: Wondering if Principal Financial Group is still a smart buy at today's price, or if the big gains are already behind it? You are not alone, and that is exactly what we are going to unpack. The stock has climbed 1.5% over the last week, 6.0% over the past month, and is now up 15.7% year to date, building on a strong 20.0% gain over the last year and 126.3% over five years. Those moves have come as investors reassess financials that can hold up in different market conditions and rotate back...
